data.description: Lovingly maintained and packed with updates! Must see this super cute cape cod. New Kitchen, New bath, new deck! Newer roof and mechanics.  Plenty of off-street parking and oversized garage. Fenced in yard.  Great location close to everything the westside has to offer and a short zip to downtown.  Walking distance to park. Partially finished lower level can be additional bedroom or bonus room.  Come fall in love with this squeaky clean 3 bedroom charmer.
